    Goal: Demonstrate full development cycle: REST API, authentication, documentation, CI/CD.

    Functionality:

        Registration/login with JWT.

        CRUD for projects and tasks.

        User roles (admin, user).

        Swagger/OpenAPI documentation.

    Technologies: Spring Boot, Spring Security, JPA + MS SQL, Docker Compose, Testcontainers.

    What it demonstrates: Ability to build secure REST APIs and test them comprehensively.
